@startuml HealthBank_Participant_Survey_Sequence
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #2C76BF
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #595959
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #1A1A2E
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #EBF4FF
skinparam shadowing false
autoactivate off

title HealthBank — Participant Completes a Survey

actor       "Participant"      as P
participant "Flutter App"      as APP
participant "FastAPI\n/api/v1" as API
database    "MySQL"            as DB

== Open Assigned Survey ==

P -> APP : Navigate to Tasks / Dashboard
APP -> API : GET /api/v1/assignments?status=pending
API -> DB  : SELECT SurveyAssignment JOIN Survey\nWHERE AccountID=? AND Status='pending'
DB --> API : list of assignments
API --> APP : List<SurveyAssignment>
APP --> P  : Show pending task cards

P -> APP : Tap "Do Task" on a survey
APP -> API : GET /api/v1/surveys/{id}/questions
API -> DB  : SELECT QuestionBank, QuestionOptions, QuestionList\nWHERE SurveyID=? ORDER BY DisplayOrder
DB --> API : questions with options
API --> APP : List<Question>
APP --> P  : Render question form\n(scale / yesno / single_choice / multi_choice / number / openended)

== Answer & Draft Save ==

P -> APP : Fill in answers as they go
APP -> API : POST /api/v1/responses/draft\n{ assignment_id, responses: [...] }
API -> DB  : UPDATE SurveyAssignment\nSET DraftResponses = ?\nWHERE AssignmentID = ?
DB --> API : 1 row updated
API --> APP : 200 { "saved": true }
APP --> P  : Silent autosave (no UI interruption)

note over P, APP : Participant can close app and return.\nDraft is restored from SurveyAssignment.DraftResponses.

== Final Submission ==

P -> APP : Tap "Submit"
APP -> APP : Validate all required questions answered
alt Required question missing
  APP --> P : Highlight unanswered question\n"This question is required"
else All required answered
  APP -> API : POST /api/v1/responses\n{ assignment_id,\n  responses: [{ question_id, value }] }
  API -> DB  : BEGIN TRANSACTION\nINSERT INTO Responses (SurveyID, ParticipantID,\n  QuestionID, ResponseValue)\nFOR EACH response\nUPDATE SurveyAssignment\n  SET Status='completed', CompletedAt=NOW()\nCOMMIT
  DB --> API : responses stored, assignment updated
  API --> APP : 201 { "submitted": true }
  APP --> P  : "Survey completed!" confirmation
  APP --> P  : Redirect to Results page
end

== View Results ==

P -> APP : Navigate to Results
P -> APP : Select completed survey
APP -> API : GET /api/v1/responses/{survey_id}
API -> DB  : SELECT ResponseValue, QuestionContent, ResponseType\nFROM Responses JOIN QuestionBank\nWHERE ParticipantID=? AND SurveyID=?
DB --> API : participant responses
API --> APP : List<ResponseSummary>
APP --> P  : Show own responses

P -> APP : Toggle "Compare to Aggregate"
APP -> API : GET /api/v1/research/surveys/{id}/aggregates
API -> DB  : SELECT per-question aggregate stats\nHAVING COUNT(DISTINCT ParticipantID) >= k
DB --> API : aggregates (suppressed where < k)
API --> APP : AggregateResponse
APP --> P  : Show side-by-side own vs. aggregate\n(suppressed questions show k-anon notice)

@enduml
